{"tid":1423004,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國眾議院議長: 支持香港示威者 兩黨會推動香港人權與民主法案","createTime":"2019-08-06T12:36:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T23:11:58.000Z","uid":54733,"like":445,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":109,"replies":[{"pid":"331836e1c219ec9393878fbccc0fff653e97f557","tid":1423004,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:36:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=piatLX99YjU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DpiatLX99YjU&d=I5RPnmyQkmy%2BYB%2FsDyc%2Bv3WT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=96f1f42e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=piatLX99YjU</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】美國眾議院議長佩洛西發表聲明，支持香港「反送中」示威者，兩黨議員將在國會復會後，推動香港人權與民主法案。<br />\n<br />\n佩洛西說入夏以來，香港人一直向全世界發出一個激動人心的訊息，就是自由、正義和民主的理想，永不會被威嚇和不公義澆滅。<br />\n<br />\n她又說香港人表現出極大勇氣，跟拒絕尊重法治、不願履行一國兩制義務的懦弱政府，形成極其鮮明的對比，香港立法會應立即徹底、並永久撤銷逃犯條例修訂工作。<br />\n<br />\n她指民主共和兩黨的國會議員將在九月，國會休會期結束後，開始推動香港人權與民主法案，為保香港民主自由和法治奮鬥。<br />\n<br />\n外交部駐港特派員公署強烈譴責佩洛西公然支持暴力抗法分子，粗暴干預香港事務和中國內政，中方對此表示強烈不滿和堅決反對。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=358185\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D358185&d=I5RPnmyQkmy%2BYB%2FsDyc%2Bv3WT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=d3061023\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D358185&h=4c7c7e1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=358185</a>"},{"pid":"b1e364acce66a0cdcf94f4b0603b2a79c612aed0","tid":1423004,"uid":251119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:37:56.000Z","msg":"[回應同警察傾計個post] 警世，終於知道點解連登仔咁易比人帶到風向<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1422798\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1422798</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8b038522e556ea5b2bc68bc822bfa75954526a3f","tid":1423004,"uid":251119,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:38:10.000Z","msg":"this way sir"},{"pid":"25185809dc945c6fdd26823f92a4de8d2c336d1e","tid":1423004,"uid":54733,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:39:14.000Z","msg":"香港人權與民主法案係兩黨共識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"746239b491d7f2cd1d20e995ea3f0912323dffd7","tid":1423004,"uid":130421,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:39:30.000Z","msg":"咁多位手足<br />\n一齊頂落去<br />\n就會成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfc5e94ec06bc0df128fe0ce2aac6b02b6a89faf","tid":1423004,"uid":145558,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:40:58.000Z","msg":"黎啦 就黎頂唔撚緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0153df8cd5334d6a558d4a3c9cfd7768a731351b","tid":1423004,"uid":290176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:41:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b83247a298546ac9caf63340d99bc91f1cfecd51","tid":1423004,"uid":191926,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:43:32.000Z","msg":"佩洛西<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n魯比奧<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n蓬皮奧<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佩斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bfae6085df53ecb5e143ef093d6604080fd904a","tid":1423004,"uid":34140,"like":64,"dislike":0,"score":64,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:43:51.000Z","msg":"美國: 喺自己國家立條得美國先適用嘅法案<br />\n強国: 粗暴干涉中國同香港內政<br />\n香港人: sir this way<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bbf314ce70811ce284679729020ba1e1dbeae8d","tid":1423004,"uid":143183,"like":6,"disl